    th_package_search.Rd

    Searches for packages satisfying a given search criteria.

    Usage

    th_package_search(keyword, as_dataframe = TRUE)

    Arguments

    keyword

    keyword to search

    as_dataframe

    logical value whether to simplify the result into a data.frame object. Default as TRUE.

    Examples

    # ASCII values means COVID in Thai
th_package_search(keyword = intToUtf8(c(3650L, 3588L, 3623L, 3636L, 3604L)))
